{"tid":612411,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"癡人說夢，拋磚引玉，希望可以激發大家為香港另闢前路","createTime":"2018-03-31T20:42:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-02T15:37:33.000Z","uid":104443,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7702af89bab5145d4575987bfa530a03625f1d00","tid":612411,"uid":104443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T20:42:15.000Z","msg":"以下內容可能大家會認為我係癡人說夢，誠然港獨原意係好，而且亦係對香港人最好嘅選擇，但係共匪實在太強大，文武兼備，要槍有槍，要炮有炮，我哋必須考慮到自己究竟有冇足夠力量成功令香港獨立，抑或只係流於理想之中，以宜家大部分香港人嘅生活水平，究竟有幾多人願意為對抗中共而犧牲自我？肯定有，但亦係少數。<br />\n<br />\n大家請睇下中華民國，由1949年失去大陸江山以嚟，仍堅守到台澎金馬至今近七十載！證明消滅共匪仲存有希望！如果台灣識做嘅話，就應該持續強化軍備，準備他日同共匪決一死戰！收復大陸河山！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請大家支持香港回歸中華民國！匯聚全港民意向臨時首都台北之總統府請願！與其等到2047年等死，不如回歸中華民國！咁對香港亦未嘗係好選擇！況且中華民國先係正統中國，法理上亦有權收回香港！本人再一次請大家支持香港回歸中華民國！中華民國萬歲！共匪必須被消滅！我笑住睇班五毛橫屍街頭！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">中華民國萬歲！<br />\n正統中國萬歲！<br />\n三民主義萭歲！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/24/002715_a3fa723bda0c29665bda8848c00790f7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F24%2F002715_a3fa723bda0c29665bda8848c00790f7.png&h=2c89cbe0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">反對共匪（陸獨），反對台獨，中華民國先係中國正統！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/24/002812_bd33e163a9fc2e9371e158940b0fbf3f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F24%2F002812_bd33e163a9fc2e9371e158940b0fbf3f.png&h=93fc6b91&s={SIZE}\" />[/red]"},{"pid":"036f4037d7eb7006f267864d1f68f61e44d27d8c","tid":612411,"uid":104443,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T20:44:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">中華民國萬歲萬歲萬萬歲！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"d9d7b984e6c0fe81751e4cb967aae1eeca5bb1a6","tid":612411,"uid":2436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T21:09:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"36d7581120a227e443c2b322780c7cf9a2f4e0c5","tid":612411,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T23:41:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"877c3cf6aa4ed9106c9592f801f01770df9a0ba1","tid":612411,"uid":104443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T05:23:16.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"610e92b695c05850acbb0e2fb2581773eec207f8","tid":612411,"uid":104443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T05:27:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">法理上中華民國亦有《南京條約》正本，絕對有權收回香港！香港回歸中華民國先係最好選擇！</span>"},{"pid":"f792ad72021218adc8f9b2a292693e9941cce11b","tid":612411,"uid":104443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T05:32:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1dc8e6efb78956065c350ec2ef02eac56dbb22c","tid":612411,"uid":172497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T05:34:21.000Z","msg":"你都1000歲啦，唔好搞咁多野啦<br />\n你不如同宋朝請願叫佢收返香港啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5ee34651b42dd9d33294f30f7438157cf34f01a","tid":612411,"uid":104443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1dc8e6efb78956065c350ec2ef02eac56dbb22c","tid":612411,"uid":172497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T05:34:21.000Z","msg":"你都1000歲啦，唔好搞咁多野啦<br />\n你不如同宋朝請願叫佢收返香港啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T05:45:59.000Z","msg":"中華民國係當今同共匪最敵對，而且係共匪敵對關係之中最有力量反擊嘅國家！退一步講，比中華民國統治香港肯定比共匪好好多，我地要面對現